{
  "stem": "747.4",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So when they came, this old Wehrmacht soldier, he was an elderly man, looking for workers to-- made a group of 20 women.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I, of course, I wanted to go.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So he picked me, and took us out to clean the watchtowers around the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And the four corners, four-- five girls to a corner-- to a tower.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "That was four corners.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We were supposed to wash the floor and wash the windows, and clean up.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "It wasn't much to do.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "Now he, as we find out later on, he made this kommando for his own interest.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He was getting out the hard liquor to the crematorium, to the people, to the sonderkommando who was working there.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And in return for the favor, because these guys couldn't work-- I mean, it was just unbelievable, painful, to see.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Sometimes they find their own relatives among the dead.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, they were the one who had to separate the bodies, and put them into the oven and burn them.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And the ashes, whatever-- I don't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "If I would know exactly, I wouldn't be able to tell you, because nobody came out from there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I can just tell you what I saw over the fence from the watchtower.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We saw what went on in the yard, in the front of the crematorium.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So this guy, this Wehrmacht soldier, he was-- he was not bad.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He didn't hurt us, but he had his own interest, why he-- he did what he did.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He carried out the liquor-- nobody checked him over.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he sold it for this sonderkommando, this man who worked inside.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And for the favor, for-- he got all the jewelries and gold from the teeth, what they pulled out from the dead bodies, and whatever they find in the clothes.",
      "word_count": 30
    }
  ],
